      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "史文恭"
      ],
      "text": "某，史文恭。自幼曾拜周侗为师，习练全身武艺。只因梁山贼寇，恃蛮横行，每每打家劫舍，扰害黎民。前有段景住，在口外得了一匹好马，名为追风千里驹，曾要献与宋江，那时他打从我庄经过，被某将此马夺来。谁想那段景住，去至梁山，搬动是非。那晁盖带领人马前来，是俺一箭，将他射死，梁山众贼寇，定必要与他报仇。俺也曾命庄丁暗地打探，未见回报到来。",
      "text_length": 164
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00005",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四下手、四英雄暗同上。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00006",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "史文恭"
      ],
      "text": "左右，",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00007",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00008",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "史文恭"
      ],
      "text": "伺候了。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00009",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "八庄丁同上。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00010",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "同念",
      "speakers": [
        "八庄丁"
      ],
      "text": "忙将梁山事，报与庄主知。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00011",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "八庄丁"
      ],
      "text": "参见庄主。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00012",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "史文恭"
      ],
      "text": "尔等回来了？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00013",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "八庄丁"
      ],
      "text": "回来了。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00014",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "史文恭"
      ],
      "text": "打探梁山之事，怎么样了？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00015",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "八庄丁"
      ],
      "text": "今有宋江，拜卢俊义为帅，带领忠义堂众好汉，一并前来，要扰乱我庄。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00016",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "史文恭"
      ],
      "text": "那梁山贼寇，要扰乱我庄？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00017",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "八庄丁"
      ],
      "text": "正是。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00018",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "史文恭"
      ],
      "text": "想那卢俊义，与俺同窗学艺，他若前来拜庄，速报我知。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00019",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "吓！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00020",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "史文恭下，众人同随下。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00021",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四龙套、四上手、二女将、阮小二、阮小五、三将、林冲、燕青、武松、卢俊义同上。",
      "text_length": 38
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00022",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "卢俊义"
      ],
      "text": "众位哥嫂请了。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00023",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "请了。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00024",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "卢俊义"
      ],
      "text": "我等奉了大哥将令，来到此处，待俺随同林贤弟与燕小哥，前去拜庄。众家哥嫂，在庄外埋伏不得有误。",
      "text_length": 46
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00025",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "得令！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00026",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "二女将、阮小二、阮小五、三将、武松同下，龙套、上手同转场。",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00027",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "燕青"
      ],
      "text": "有人么，走出一个来！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00028",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "家将上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00029",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "家将"
      ],
      "text": "什么人？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00030",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "燕青"
      ],
      "text": "卢俊义前来拜庄。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00031",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "家将"
      ],
      "text": "候着。有请庄主。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00032",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四下手、四英雄、史文恭同上。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00033",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "史文恭"
      ],
      "text": "何事？",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00034",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "副净"
      ],
      "text": "卢俊义前来拜庄。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00035",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "史文恭"
      ],
      "text": "有请。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00036",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "副净"
      ],
      "text": "有请。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00037",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "史文恭"
      ],
      "text": "吓，师兄。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00038",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "卢俊义",
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "（贤弟）（师兄）。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00039",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "史文恭"
      ],
      "text": "请坐。未知师兄贤弟驾到，某家未曾远迎，面前恕罪。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00040",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "卢俊义"
      ],
      "text": "岂敢。愚兄来得卤莽，贤弟海涵。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00041",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "史文恭"
      ],
      "text": "岂敢。吓，师兄为何这样打扮？",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00042",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "卢俊义"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟有所不知，只因梁山及时雨宋公明，招贤纳士，结交天下英雄，除暴安良，替天行道，特命愚兄前来，邀请贤弟，同上梁山，安享富贵。",
      "text_length": 62
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00043",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "史文恭"
      ],
      "text": "师兄此言差矣。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00044",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "卢俊义"
      ],
      "text": "不差。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00045",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "史文恭"
      ],
      "text": "想你我弟兄三人，同拜周侗为师，同窗学艺，练就全身武艺，谁不闻名丧胆。林贤弟因被奸臣所害，无处可归，投奔梁山躲避，事出无奈。想师兄久居大名，家财万贯，坐享安乐，为何也投那梁山贼寇！",
      "text_length": 89
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00046",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "卢俊义"
      ],
      "text": "只因你将晁天王射死，忠义堂好汉，纷纷议论。你若执意不肯归顺，梁山众弟兄，就要报那一箭之仇！",
      "text_length": 45
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00047",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "史文恭"
      ],
      "text": "师兄吓！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00048",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "急三枪",
      "speakers": [
        "史文恭"
      ],
      "text": "一箭仇，却因为相争斗。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00049",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "卢俊义"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟，事要三思，免生后悔。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00050",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "史文恭"
      ],
      "text": "想俺史文恭！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00051",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "急三枪",
      "speakers": [
        "史文恭"
      ],
      "text": "俺全凭枪法优，纵有梁山贼寇，凭来将，俺相候，哪怕你人马稠。",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00052",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "卢俊义"
      ],
      "text": "好言相劝，执意不听，少时被擒，悔之晚矣！",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00053",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "史文恭"
      ],
      "text": "听你之言，敢么是要与小弟较量么？",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00054",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "卢俊义"
      ],
      "text": "正是要与你这匹夫比试。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00055",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "史文恭"
      ],
      "text": "哪个是匹夫？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00056",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "卢俊义"
      ],
      "text": "你是匹夫。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00057",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "史文恭"
      ],
      "text": "你是匹夫。来打！（史文恭、卢俊义、林冲同起打，打群场，众人同下。史文恭、卢俊义比枪，打快枪，夺枪双扯下。燕青上，对八庄丁，败下，众人同追下。燕青出庄，家将上。）",
      "text_length": 80
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00058",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "家将"
      ],
      "text": "众庄丁，好生把守庄门。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00059",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "家将下，四上手、二女将、三将、武松同上，燕青上。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00060",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "燕青"
      ],
      "text": "众家弟兄一同前往！（四上手、二女将、三将、燕青同下，武松耍刀下。众人同上，会阵打连环，同下。史文恭、卢俊义夺枪同扯上，起打，卢俊义看。）",
      "text_length": 68
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00061",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "史文恭"
      ],
      "text": "你敢么是怯战么？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00062",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "卢俊义"
      ],
      "text": "看天色已晚，你我明日再战。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00063",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "史文恭"
      ],
      "text": "来者？",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00064",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "卢俊义"
      ],
      "text": "君子。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00065",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "史文恭"
      ],
      "text": "不来？",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00066",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "卢俊义"
      ],
      "text": "小人。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00067",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "史文恭"
      ],
      "text": "请！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00068",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "卢俊义、众人同下。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00069",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "史文恭"
      ],
      "text": "众庄丁，后面歇息。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00070",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人同下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00071",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "史文恭"
      ],
      "text": "且住，我与那卢俊义，数载不见，他的枪法越发精壮了，待等明日前来，只怕此庄有些难保。",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00072",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "史文恭拉势子。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00073",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "风入松",
      "speakers": [
        "史文恭"
      ],
      "text": "我看他枪法，甚是高强，盘旋围绕似秋霜。任你英雄武艺壮，怎当俺横冲直撞。好一似搅海翻江，管叫你一命亡。",
      "text_length": 50
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00074",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "史文恭"
      ],
      "text": "我看他等初到此处，未必准备，不免三更时分，偷营劫寨便了。",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00075",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "史文恭拉势，下。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00076",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "卢俊义、众人同上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00077",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "卢俊义"
      ],
      "text": "众弟兄，今晚要饱餐战饭，谨慎小心防备那贼前来劫寨。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00078",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李逵"
      ],
      "text": "大家小心了！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00079",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "史文恭、众人同上，起打八股荡，史文恭败下。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00080",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "阮小二、阮小五同上。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00081",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "阮小二"
      ],
      "text": "我，追魂太岁阮小二。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00082",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 82,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "阮小五"
      ],
      "text": "我，短命二郎阮小五。哥哥，你我奉了大哥之命扮做打鱼的模样，等候史文恭，你我就此前往。",
      "text_length": 42
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00083",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 83,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "阮小二、阮小五同下。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00084",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 84,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "史文恭上，翻跟头。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00085",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 85,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "史文恭"
      ],
      "text": "卢俊义十分骁勇，待我逃走。吓，渔船快快摆过来！",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00086",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 86,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "阮小二、阮小五同上。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00087",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 87,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "阮小二",
        "阮小五"
      ],
      "text": "我们是打鱼的船，不渡人。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00088",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 88,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "史文恭"
      ],
      "text": "多把银钱与你。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00089",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 89,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "阮小二",
        "阮小五"
      ],
      "text": "多给银钱就好，待我搭了扶手。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00090",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 90,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "史文恭上船，上桌。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00091",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 91,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "阮小二",
        "阮小五"
      ],
      "text": "船到了江心，给钱罢。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00092",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 92,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "史文恭"
      ],
      "text": "到岸再给。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00093",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 93,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "阮小二",
        "阮小五"
      ],
      "text": "不行！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01019009_e00094",
      "play_id": "01019009",
      "scene_id": "01019009_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 94,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "史文恭推阮小二、阮小五下水，阮小二、阮小五同扯史文恭下，对打，史文恭被擒。",
      "text_length": 37
    }
  ],
  "roles_inferred": true
